    bf:summary [ a bf:Summary ;
            rdfs:label "Black Pawl and his son, Red Pawl, are the captain and first mate of a schooner on which comes Helene Chadwick, looking for passage back to the states. There is plenty of anger and action from a rebellious crew in this melodrama."@en ] ;
